      "description": "2019 sedan in fair condition. The exterior has some scratches and minor dents, with light surface rust in a couple of areas. The interior shows moderate wear \u2014 upholstery has some scuffing and minor damage to a few components. Mechanically functional with no major issues noted, though the car shows its age in appearance.",
