      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable ride or a hands-on project? This vehicle is priced to reflect its current condition \u2014 it shows significant wear both inside and out, and will likely need some mechanical attention to get it running at its best. That said, it's a great opportunity for a mechanically inclined buyer looking to save big upfront. Grab it while it's available at this wallet-friendly price!",
